35:45.610 --> 35:49.981 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID LORDKIPANIDZE: I think
they were both.
On the bones of the humans, you
can sometimes

35:50.015 --> 35:56.187 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
