I think main
human character is the
curiosity.

37:36.821 --> 37:41.259 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: So this is the
same instinct
that we have today, to look
around the next

37:41.292 --> 37:42.794 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
corner, over the next hill.

37:42.827 --> 37:44.395 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DAVID LORDKIPANIDZE: Paul is
doing the same.

37:44.429 --> 37:46.097 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: As these guys
did.

37:46.131 --> 37:50.001 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID LORDKIPANIDZE: As these
guys did. Paul
is follower of Homo erectus.

37:50.034 --> 37:51.836 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

37:51.870 --> 37:55.173 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And, in a
