we all. But for Salopek, their
ancient journey

37:55.206 --> 37:57.408 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to this point has particular
meaning.

37:57.442 --> 38:00.845 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SALOPEK: These are the
first pioneer
wanderers. These are kind of
like the dawn

38:00.879 --> 38:06.651 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
