wine maker had sunk his vat.

38:25.503 --> 38:28.239 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID LORDKIPANIDZE: You can see
1.8 million
years old.

38:28.273 --> 38:30.608 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The bone is
1.8 million
years old.

38:30.642 --> 38:36.080 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, in the process, that person
