recently, Russia.

39:41.179 --> 39:45.850 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
They have overlapped and
contested and fought
over this corner of the world
for centuries.

39:45.883 --> 39:48.253 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: So, if they
have lived here,
they have also died here.

39:48.286 --> 39:51.356 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SALOPEK: A lot of people
have died here
over the years. I think we're
standing on

39:51.389 --> 39:53.224 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
