40:50.281 --> 40:54.719 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL POLLAN, Author, "In
Defense of Food":
I have been writing about the
food system

40:54.752 --> 41:00.124 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
for a very long time, but what I
kept hearing
from readers was, yes, yes, yes,
you have

41:00.158 --> 41:03.328 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
