The food industry has gotten
incredibly food
at manipulating the properties
of food, so

41:20.178 --> 41:26.217 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
it has just the right texture,
just the right
color, just the right smell.

41:26.250 --> 41:28.753 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But we have been paying a heavy
price.

41:28.786 --> 41:35.159 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Four of the top 10 things that
will kill you
are chronic diseases linked to
diet.

41:35.193 --> 41:41.432 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN: We're dealing with a crisis
that's at
an emergency level. Their lives
are at stake.

41:41.466 --> 41:43.935 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I think all of our lives are at
stake.

41:43.968 --> 41:48.406 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN: We are looking for answers.
We are looking
for dietary salvation.

41:48.439 --> 41:57.715 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL POLLAN: So I studied the
science from
Tanzania to Peru, from Paris to
the Bronx.

41:57.749 --> 42:00.084 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MAN: Let's walk our way through
this.

42:00.118 --> 42:02.954 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICHAEL POLLAN: And what I
discovered will
surprise you.

42:02.987 --> 42:06.157 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN: You don't have to be a
